      "content": "hey my left eye is super red and it's kinda hurting a bit. there's also this weird crusty stuff in it when i wake up. i've been staring at my laptop way too much lately so i think it's just really bad dry eyes. do u think i can just get some of those regular lube eye drops from the pharmacy and it'll go away?",
