      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i aint got time to go to a clinic right now and it's so expensive here. surely if i just use some intense lubricating drops every hour or so it'll clear up the irritation? i really dont think it's anything serious like pink eye, it just feels scratchy from the screen.",
